1. alsa.conf

	$ sudo sh -c "printf 'pcm.0.card 0 pcm.0.device 0 pcm.0.subdevice 0 pcm.0.type hw defaults.pcm.minperiodtime 2772    ;  ' > /usr/share/alsa/alsa.conf.min"

2. Config files

	$ sudo nano *.conf (mpd, upmpdcli, mympd, roon, spotifyd)

		quadruple-space+line feed+double-space at the end without new line
